    clear_dialog
    talk sinner talk "GHOST?"
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        "Your companions voice echoes through the cavern. Above you. Above you."
        "[Splash about and break through the surface of the water]":
            talk sinner talk "GHOST IS THAT YOU!?"
        "<span class='magenta'>[MAGENTA MAGENTA MAGENTA MAGENTA]</span>":
            jump woods_magenta_end 
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        "You burst out of the water, spluttering, your arms flail pathetically. You cannot stay afloat. Again you sink."
        "[Gasp for air]":
            "You gasp desperately for oxygen, but there is only <span class='magenta'>magenta</span>. <span class='magenta'>Magenta magenta magenta magenta.</span>"
            clear_dialog
            "<span class='magenta'>Magenta</span>, and then nothing."
            clear_dialog
            stop music
            stop ambient 1
            stop ambient 2
            stop ambient 3
            stop ambient 4
            stop ambient 5
            run transition_instant generic_black
            wait 4000
            run transition cave_lake
            "Oestradiol smoke, girl musk, moss."
            "The Sinner has dragged you out of the water. She is soaking wet."
            clear_dialog
            choice:
                talk sinner talk "Aha. <span class='magenta'>Magenta...</span>"
                "\\"Are you okay?\\"":
                    "The Sinner looks right through you."
                "\\"<span class='magenta'>Magenta...</span>\\"":
                    "The Sinner looks right through you."
            choice:
                talk sinner talk "I've fled judgement for so long, Ghost, but all this time I was wrong. There is no Hel in my future. We're already there. You and me. We all are. We are already there Ghost, and yet I creep ever on."
                "\\"When the writhing comes it will be bliss, methinks.\\"":
                    choice:
                        talk sinner talk "Our sins are ours to bare. Our hearts weigh heavy, but only we need carry them. Tell me, Ghost, do you have the will to go on?"
                        "[Nod] \\"It's why I came back. Back to the writhing. It's what we deserve, I think, but I do not want it to end. The dream is a thousand miles of razor wire, but there's such wonderful clocky dolls to dull the blades...\\"":
                            talk sinner talk "Absolution is too good for us. To suffer together is all we have..."
    clear_dialog
    wait 4000
    choice:
        "You sit with her, wet through with cold water. A shiver. The Sinner puts an arm around you. It doesn't warm you up, the woman is practically cold blooded, but it warms your heart."
        "\\"I meant what I said about clocky dolls making it all worth it. Walk with me tomorrow morning, please. It was nice to walk today, and I'd like to do it again, but not get soggy and have my brain scrambled by the realisation that guilt and sorrow is all that we are this time.\\"":
            set data.ending.presentSinner true
            add data.dream.womenOptions 1
            talk sinner talk "A walk... yes..."
            clear_dialog
            "She <span class='goldItalic'>smiles</span> at you."
            clear_dialog
            talk sinner talk "If it is our destiny to live in horror, let us make the most of it."
            clear_dialog
            "<span class='goldItalic'>Perhaps women and walks through the woods are the closest to forgiveness we can come?</span>"
            "<span class='magenta'>The dolls may crumble and the woods may burn one day,</span><span class='goldItalic'> but for now they too endure.</span>"
            clear_dialog
            wait 4000
    if (&& (== $data.sinner.reading "hrt") (!= (has_item? hrt) true)):
        choice:
            talk sinner talk "The other day you asked about hormones, didn't you, Ghost? You sought knowledge from the cards."
            "\\"I might have done. I'll be honest my memory is pretty goofy.\\"":
                talk sinner talk "Lunden Road. Sundown. The moon shall guide your way."
                clear_dialog
                "She peers down at you, and cocks her head."
                clear_dialog
                choice:
                    talk sinner talk "The Pale Spectre hath spoketh. The Moon cometh."
                    "\\"Oh. I already knew that. Thanks though.\\"" if (objective_started? hrt dealer):
                        "The Sinner looks a little upset."
                        if (roll woods_pit_useful_lovely lovely 40):
                            talk lovely talk "<span class='writtenText'>'I really am useless, aren't I?'</span>"
                        else:
                            wait 1000
                    "[Nod] \\"Okay. I follow\\"" if (!= (objective_started? hrt dealer) true):
                        run skip
    clear_dialog
    "The Sinner shivers. It is chilly out, and she is very thin. Still, she manages a small <span class='goldItalic'>smile</span> back."
    clear_dialog
    stop sound 2
    complete_objective sinner woods
    complete_quest sinner sinnerSuccessMagenta
    jump goToGameMap

